div.p:
I, trembling, like Endymion over-bent

By dazzling Dian, when, with wonderment

He saw her crescent light the Latmian lea;

A remarkably clever jeu d'esprit after the fashion of “Rejec-

ted Addresses.” The authors introduced are Croaker & Co.;

Daniel Webster; Longfellow; Willis; Irving; Morris;

Woodworth; Halleck; Bryant; McDonald Clarke; and two

others whom we do not recognize.
